
Requirement:
1. As a customer I should be able to see restaurants in the locality, their menus.
2. As a customer I should be able to select food items and add them to cart.
3. As a customer I should be able to place order.
4. As a customer I should be able to receive notification/update regarding my order.
5. As a platform app should drop the order to restaurant.
6. As a platform delivery app should be able to assign delivery person to the order.
7. As a platform app should update/notify user with the order updates.

Actors:
1. Customer/User
2. Restaurant
3. Delivery Person
4. App System
